title: Paul Ryan says he'll be Speaker of the House (maybe): What they're saying
text: Paul Ryan says he'll be Speaker of the House (maybe): What they're saying Paul Ryan Rep. Paul Ryan, R- Wis., arrives at a news conference following a House Republican meeting, Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, on Capitol Hill in Washington. Ryan told GOP lawmakers that he will run for speaker, but only if they embrace him by week's end as their consensus candidate, an ambitious bid to impose unity on a disordered and divided House. (Andrew Harnik / AP)
